Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:16.18,INJ,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}暗夜航路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:18.77,INJ,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}灯火
